經驗完左可以去刷每日強襲角，知、速角優先，刷的意思係講每隻刷10隻刷到10技，再刷多隻5技放倉，準備以後解超強襲.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n角色代號<br />\n感謝 格劍巴整合代號名單 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rncalhpj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frncalhpj&h=e1d19c4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊代號名單 感謝 photomore 巴打整合 <br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg&d=rtu48TbBxRTlrxDLd9TUuI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0a1d3a5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n限定點心紙<br />\n感謝 願你今夜別離去巴打整合<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3a7jv78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3a7jv78.jpg&h=6489d757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超激時間表<br />\n感謝 願你今夜別離去巴打整合<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gY57fC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgY57fC7.jpg&h=0b84a2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抽卡前請三思<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/032521_d685e28f3afbcdf8018b432c06024774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F032521_d685e28f3afbcdf8018b432c06024774.jpg&h=ecb7e40d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2389a4a12e69bd9c23881fb2b07895574d8df714","tid":258342,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">感謝早妃巴打提供</span></span><br />\n抽卡前請三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm